session-variable.name: EBS_INSTANCE
session-variable.query: SELECT profile_option_value FROM fnd_profile_option_values WHERE profile_option_id= (SELECT profile_option_id FROM fnd_profile_options WHERE profile_option_name = 'APPS_FRAMEWORK_AGENT') AND level_value = 0

session-variable.name: MULTIPLE_ORGS
session-variable.query: select org_id from ra_cust_trx_line_gl_dist_all where rownum < 2

session-variable.name: MyOrganizations
session-variable.query: select distinct oav.organization_id from org_access_v oav, fnd_user_resp_groups_direct furg, fnd_user fu where fu.user_id = furg.user_id and oav.responsibility_id = furg.responsibility_id and fu.user_name=upper($userid) order by 1

session-variable.name: MyPersonId
session-variable.query: select distinct(er.miniteamid) from erperson er , person p where er.personid=p.personid and p.cpersonid = $personid and $user <> 'super@incorta.com' and $user <>'400apple' union select -1 from dual where $user='super@incorta.com'

session-variable.name: MyUserId
session-variable.query: select cast($user as int) from dual

session-variable.name: TEST_SESSION_VARIABLE
session-variable.query: select SUM(PROJECT_TO_DATE_CR ) FROM GL_BALANCES WHERE LEDGER_ID = $MULTIPLE_ORGS

session-variable.name: TestingSessionV
session-variable.query: select to_char(1) from dual where $user=1165 and $user <>'super@incorta.com' union select '*' from dual where $user='super@incorta.com'

session-variable.name: currentMonthSeq
session-variable.description: Return the sequence number for current month

session-variable.name: currentWeekSeq
session-variable.description: Return the sequence number for the current week

session-variable.name: currentYearSeq
session-variable.description: Return the sequence number of current year

session-variable.name: personid
session-variable.query: select to_char(personid) from person where cpersonid=$user and $user <>'super@incorta.com' and $user<>'400apple' union select '*' from dual where ($user='super@incorta.com' or $user='400apple')
